data.description: Nice 4 plex in a quiet neighborhood with quick freeway access. 2 blocks from a riverside park. Shopping, restaurants and bus stop in close proximity. All units are currently occupied w/ fenced common lawn and garden area. Decks/patios. 2 of the units have been recently updated. Possible 5th unit/ADA potential. Buyer due diligence.  Laundry is onsite.
